```
# Rust/Cargo specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock

# Compiled and build artifacts
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.rlib
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/*.dll
**/*.exe
**/*.dSYM/

# Dependencies
vendor/
.cargo/

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```